' is banned in <LOCATION> Egypt </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Iran </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> India </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Pakistan </LOCATION> and several other countries. At least 18 people have died in protests against the book in <LOCATION> India </LOCATION> and <LOCATION> Pakistan </LOCATION>.
